Feb. 11, 1984 D Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival (Third Section)
Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival (Third Section) 30 Entertainments Contest Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival milton-keynes-brass-band-festival-third-section
Stantonbury Leisure Centre Sports Hall, Milton Keynes Bands played an entertainment programme including Torch Of Freedom. 11 bands competed. Best Instrumentalist: Euphonium, Kidderminster
1st Prize: £100.00 (Copperad trophy) 2nd Prize: £60.00 (Festival trophy) 3rd Prize: £35.00 (Audi trophy) 4th Prize: £25.00
